OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776089466
OL,3,CAverage UK household will be #480
OL,4,Cworse off this year due to Middle East
OL,5,Cwar
OL,7,FHigher global energy prices triggered
OL,8,Fby the ongoing war in the Middle East
OL,9,Fcould leave the average working-aged
OL,10,FBritish household #480 worse off this
OL,11,Fyear, a think tank has warned.
OL,13,FWhile some lower-income households
OL,14,Fhave received long-overdue real-terms
OL,15,Fincrease in their benefits, average
OL,16,Fincome growth for the poorest fifth is
OL,17,Fnow set to be just 1.2% ` down from
OL,18,F2.8% before the conflict with Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776089466
OL,3,CAverage UK household will be #480
OL,4,Cworse off this year due to Middle East
OL,5,Cwar
OL,7,FThat's according to the Resolution
OL,8,FFoundation think tank, which says that
OL,9,Fwhile the future of the conflict
OL,10,Fremains uncertain, large falls in
OL,11,Fenergy prices the increased cost of
OL,12,Fenergy bills and petrol at the pump
OL,13,Fwill almost certainly be passed on to
OL,14,Fhouseholds.
OL,16,FThe typical household, previously on
OL,17,Ftrack for a 0.9 per cent growth in
OL,18,Fliving standards, is now set to see
OL,19,Fits income fall by 0.6 per cent ` a
OL,20,Fdifference of #480 ` over the course
OL,21,Fof the current financial year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776089466
OL,3,CAverage UK household will be #480
OL,4,Cworse off this year due to Middle East
OL,5,Cwar
OL,7,FThe picture is brighter for families
OL,8,Fin the bottom half of income
OL,9,Fdistribution with three or more
OL,10,Fchildren, however, as even after an
OL,11,Finflation shock, the abolition of the
OL,12,Ftwo-child limit is estimated to
OL,13,Fdeliver 7.7% income growth for this
OL,14,Fdemographic this year.
OL,16,FIn comparison, income growth of the
OL,17,Fpoorer families with fewer than three
OL,18,Fchildren is expected to stagnate at
OL,19,F0%, the Resolution Foundation says.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776089466
OL,3,CAverage UK household will be #480
OL,4,Cworse off this year due to Middle East
OL,5,Cwar
OL,7,FThe independent think-tank, which aims
OL,8,Fto improve the standard of living of
OL,9,Fthose on low and middle incomes, has
OL,10,Furged the government to take action.
OL,12,FIt said ministers must accelerate work
OL,13,Fon a social tariff ahead of winter,
OL,14,Fwhen energy costs will be hit the
OL,15,Fhardest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
