FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776089466
OL,3,CAverage UK household will be #480
OL,4,Cworse off this year due to Middle East
OL,5,Cwar
OL,7,FResolution Foundation Chief Economist,
OL,8,FJames Smith, said: "Despite hopes for
OL,9,Fa sustained peace, the path of this
OL,10,Fconflict remains uncertain and energy
OL,11,Fprices remain well above pre-war
OL,12,Flevels, meaning many households face a
OL,13,Fdecline in their purchasing power this
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,26,@pD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
