FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776089466
OL,3,CAverage UK household will be #480
OL,4,Cworse off this year due to Middle East
OL,5,Cwar
OL,7,F"This squeeze will run right through
OL,8,Fthe income distribution. Lower-income
OL,9,Fhouseholds will still see some income
OL,10,Fgrowth thanks to a long-awaited rise
OL,11,Fin real benefit levels, but inflation
OL,12,Fwill likely knock more than a
OL,13,Fpercentage point off what they stood
OL,14,Fto gain.
OL,16,F"For those in the middle and towards
OL,17,Fthe top of the income distribution,
OL,18,Feven the thin growth they had been
OL,19,Fexpecting has tipped into negative
OL,20,Fterritory."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
