OL,3,CAverage UK household will be #480
OL,4,Cworse off this year due to Middle East
OL,5,Cwar
OL,7,FIt comes after Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer warned that combating the
OL,9,Feffects of the war in Iran "will not
OL,10,Fbe easy" and "will affect the future
OL,11,Fof our country".
