OL,3,CAverage UK household will be #480
OL,4,Cworse off this year due to Middle East
OL,5,Cwar
OL,7,FHowever, he insisted the UK was "well-
OL,8,Fplaced" to weather the storm `
OL,9,Fhighlighting a set of measures the
OL,10,Fgovernment was already taking to
OL,11,Fcombat the rising cost-of-living.
OL,13,FThese included cutting energy bills by
OL,14,Fover #100 per household, extending the
OL,15,Fcut in fuel duty until September, a
OL,16,F#53 million support package for
OL,17,Fconsumers relying on heating oil, and
OL,18,Finvestments in renewable energy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
