OL,3,CAverage UK household will be #480
OL,4,Cworse off this year due to Middle East
OL,5,Cwar
OL,7,F"I'm sick and tired of your energy
OL,8,Fbills fluctuating up and down because
OL,9,Fwe're on the international market," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"If we took control of our energy and
OL,13,Fhad homegrown renewables, we could
OL,14,Fstabilise your bills."
